  Koh kang2-kiu3 Sin-cheng Jit8-ki3-kou3-su7 e5 chheh; si7 kong2 chhu3-piN u7 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, eng7 chng3-a2 lai5 ui Teng-lan5 in bu2 e5 chha5-siong7. An2-ni kap ku7 e5 chheh toa7 bo5 saN-tang5, piN5-piN5 si7 Jit8-ki3-kou3-su7, put-ko3 cheng-chha sin ku7 na7-tiaN7; taN chiu7 hi2 nng7 pun2 sou2 kong2--e5, iah8 si7 ka-ki7 kan-cheng3 bo5-iaN2, in-ui7 ka-ki7 saN mau5-tun2, sin-ku7 sou2 ki3-chai3--e5, boe7 siong-hu5. Chiok-kian3 m7-thang sui5-i3 sin3 bo5 he7-loh8 e5 chap8-chheh; chhin-chhiuN7 Beng7-chu2 kong2, ¡§Chin7-sin3-su, chek-put-ju5 bu5 su.¡¨ Chiok-kian3 lang5 sou2 choe3 e5 chheh, m7-thang bo5 chim-chiok siuN7 chiu7 khi3 sin3--i. 
  Koh lun7 chiau3 lang5 e5 liu5-thoan5 sou2 kong2--e5, iah8 si7 bo5 iaN2, iau2-ku2 kong2-liau2 khah u7 oa2-li2; goa2 koh kong2 hou7-lin2 thiaN. Liu5-thoan5 chiu7-si7 kong2, Teng-lan5 pun2 tai7 put-hau3, siong5-siong5 phah i-e5 lau7-bu2; u7 chit8 jit8 Teng-lan5 ti7 soaN-teng2 chhi7 iuN5, khoaN3-kiN3 chhiu7-teng2 ou-a-bu2 ka7 thang5 chhi7 kiaN2, chap8-hun kan-khou2; chiah siuN7 kau3 i soe3-han3 e5 si5, i-e5 lau7-bu2 iah8 tek-khak chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni lai5 chhi7--i. Teh siuN7 e5 si5, oat8-thau5 koh khoaN3-kiN3 tu2-a2 siN-chhut--lai5 e5 iuN5-a2 kiaN2, siang kha choe5-choe5 kui7-loh8 ti7 i iuN5-bu2 e5 leng-piN teh chiah8-leng, sim siu7 kam2-kek, chiu7 ka-ki7 siuN7 kong2, IuN5-kiaN2 chhut-si3 chiu7 hiau2-tit kui7 i-e5 bu2, ou-a-kiaN2 khoaN3-kiN3 i-e5 bu2 kau3, chiu7 oe7 hiau2-tit hoaN-hi2 khui-chhui3 lai5 chhio3, kiah8-thau5 chhut-siaN lai5 kiaN5-le2; ui7-ho5 goa2 be7-bat chit8 pai2 kui7 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2, iah8 be7-bat chit8 pai2 chhio3-iong5 kap goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 kiaN5-le2; hoan2-tng2 khap8-tioh8 chiu7 siu7-khi3, ai3 phah chiu7 phah, ai3 me7 chiu7 me7. Chit8-si5 thian-liong5 hoat-hian7, khui-siaN ai-siong thi5-khau3, ka-ki7 oan3-hun7 kong2, Goa2 chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 khah-su ti7 khim5-siu3? Tu2-tu2 teh ai-siong thi5-khau3 e5 si5, hng7-hng7 khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 lau7-bu2 koaN7 png7 beh lai5 hou7 i chiah8, chiu7 toa7-pou7 chau2 beh khi3 ka7 i chih, i3-su3 ai3-beh heng5-hau3, m7-kaN2 siu7 i e5 lau7-bu2 e5 sang3-png7. Na7-si7 i e5 bu2 khoaN3-kiN3 Teng-lan5 toa7-pou7 chau2--lai5, ka-ki7 siuN7 tek-khak si7 Teng-lan5 siu7-khi3 i koaN7 png7 ban7 lai5 beh phah--i, chiu7 chin-kiaN, oat8-thau5 khoaN3-kiN3 sin-piN u7 chit8 e5 chui2-khut, chiu7 tio5-loh8--khi3, sin-khu sui5-si5 hoa3-choe3 chit8 te3 chha5-pang-a2. Theng3-hau7 kau3 Teng-lan5 lai5, chiu7 loh8-chui2 chhe7 bo5 lau7-bu2 e5 sin-khu, chi2 khoaN3-kiN3 chui2-tiong u7 chit8 te3 chha5-pang-a2 na7-tiaN7; chiu7 siuN7 hit-te3 chha5-pang-a2, tek-khak si7 i-e5 bu2 hoa3-sin--e5; tui3 an2-ni toa7 siaN ai-siong thi5-khau3, theh8 hit te3 chha5-pang-a