  Che si7 liu5-thoan5 e5 oe7. Haih-ah! Kho2-sioh chit-ho7 liu5-thoan5; thiaN-liau2 khiok-ia2 u7 khiok-chiat; kho2-sioh na7 beh kheng5 chin, long2 bo5 iaN2-chiah. In-ui7 tui3 kou2-cha2 i2-lai5, peng7-bo5 thiaN-kiN3 lang5 loh8 chui2-khut, sui5-si5 chiu7 oe7 hoa3 bo5--khi3; siat-su2 hit e5 sin-khu si7 choa2 kou5--e5, iah8 boe7 chit8 tiap-a2 ku2 iuN5 kau3-liau2, tiok8-toan3 bo5 chit-ho7 e5 cheng5-li2. 
  U7 lang5 khah u7 kang2-kiu3 chhim-siuN7, si7 kong2, Ki5-sit8 si7 Teng-lan5 siu7-khi3 i-e5 lau7-bu2 koaN7 png7 ban7 lai5, an2-ni chit8-si5 hoat siu7-khi3, u7 chho3-chhiu2 phah-si2 i-e5 lau7-bu2. Teng-lan5 khoaN3-kiN3 i-e5 lau7-bu2 i2-keng si2, chiu7 toa7 kiaN, in-ui7 chai i-e5 choe7 chin-tang7, koaN-hu2 tek-khak oe7 lai5 liah8 i khi3 oah8-oah8 heng5 kau3 si2. Sou2-i2 kin2-kin2 am3-chiN7 chiong i-e5 lau7-bu2 e si iam2-bat8 ti7 soaN-teng2, bo5 eng7 koan-kok i-khim; iah8 bo5 poaN3 lang5 sang3-chong3; sit8-chai7 choe7-siong7 ka-choe7, ou-hou ai-chai3 ! Teng-lan5 i2-keng phah si2 lau7-bu2 e5 choe7 sng3-si7 kek8 tang7; koh chaiN2-iuN7 jim2-tit hou7 lau7-bu2 e5 si kui thou5, bo5 eng7 koan-kok i-khim ah? Sit8 choe7-ok tho-thian. Koh Teng-lan5 i2-keng kiaN5 chiah-e5 kek8-tang7 e5 choe7 liau2, chiu7 ka-ki7 siuN7 kong2, Lang5 tek-khak oe7 phah-sng3 lau7-bu2 si7 goa2 hai7-si2--e5, iah8 soa3 biat8-si; in-ui7 na7 m7-si7 an2-ni, lau7-bu2 koaN7 png7 hou7 goa2 chiah8, thai3-oe7 u7 lai5 bo5 to3-khi3? Koh in-ui7 Teng-lan5 e5 put-hau3, si7-chhu3-piN chhin-chhek peng5-iu2 chiau5-chai, sou2-i2 na7 chhe7 bo5 i-e5 lau7-bu2, tek-khak boe7 the, kong2 m7-chai--tit. Ka-ki7 siuN7 sui-jian5 bu5-si put-kho2-cheng3, iau2-ku2 cheng3-lang5 phah-sng3 oe7 chhut; sou2-i2 siuN7 kau3 u7 chit-ho7 kan-khiau2 e5 hoat-tou7 thang chhut--lai5, ng3-bang7 oe7 moa5-phian3 cheng3-lang5. Sou2-i2 kong2 i si7 khoaN3-kiN3 khim5-siu3 e5 tai7-chi3, chit8-si5 thian-liong5 hoat-hian7 ai3-beh heng5-hau3; bo5-gi5 i bu2 ka-ki7 tioh8-kiaN, chiu7 thiau3 loh8-chui2 si2, soa3 hoa3-sin piN3 chit8 te3 chha5-pang-a2. TaN beh heng5-hau3, kho2-sioh hau3 boe7 tioh8, chiah chiong hit te3 pang-a2 theh8 to3-lai5, chhai7 ti7 thiaN-tiong e5 toh-teng2. Hit-jit8 ai-khau3 bo5 chiah8; au7-lai5 tak8 saN-tng3 beh chiah8, tioh8 seng pai5 teh hau3, jian5-au7 chiah kaN2 chiah8. An2-ni eng7 kau3 chit-ho7 toa7 kan-kui2 e5 ke3-chhek, thang hou7 lang5 bo5-gi5 i-e5 lau7-bu2 si7 i hai7-si2--e5; ou-hou ai-chai3! Teng-lan5 put-hau3 e5 choe7 si7 kek8-tang7