  In chiu7 koh kong2, Sian-siN an2-ni kong2, sit8-chai7 chin u7 li2, chiau3-lun7 Teng-lan5 si7 tai7-put-hau3. M7-ku2 au7-lai5 e5 lang5 put-ko3 si7 chit8 tiam2-sim beh ki3-liam7 na7-tiaN7; chiu7 siat-su2 chiong bok8-chu2 chhiaN2 lau5 i toh-teng2, thang hou7 choe3 kiaN2-sun e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chiu7 oe7 siuN7 tui3 pe7-bu2 chou2-kong tau khi3, in-ui7 na7 bo5 eng7 bok8-chu2, kiaN-liau2 au7-lai5 soa3 long2 boe7-ki3-tit; sou2-i2 goa2 phah-sng3 boh8-tit pai3-kui7 hok8-sai7 chiu7 ho2, chhiaN2 lau5 ti7 toh-teng2 thang khoaN3, thang choe3 ki3-liam7; kiam2 u7 sim2-mih8 siong-hai7 mah? 
  Goa2 chiu7 in3 i kong2, Na7 lau5 teh, au7-lai5 tek-khak u7 siong-hai7, li2 pun2-sin na7 bo5 koh khi3 pai3--i, chiu7 li2 e5 kiaN2-sun iah8 oe7 khi3 pai3--i. In-ui7 kau3 kiaN2-sun e5 si5, khoaN3-kiN3 pat8 lang5 teh pai3, koh khoaN3-kiN3 ka-ki7 toh-teng2 u7 bok8-chu2, tek-khak u7-si5 oe7 siu7 be5-hek8, siuN7 tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 pat8 lang5 lai5 pai3. Iah8 oe7 siuN7, na7 pai3 kaN2 bo5 siong-hai7; na7 oe7 siong-hai7, pe7-kong si7 jip8-kau3 e5 lang5, tek-khak bo5 lau5 chit-e5 mih8 ti7 toh-teng2. Sim chiu7 oe7 phah-sng3 tioh8 pai3 khah tioh8; koh in-ui7 pian7-pian7 ti7 toh-teng2, m7-sai2 lou2-lat8, chiu7 oe7 sui5-si5 khi3 pai3--i. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni au7-lai5 e5 poe7-poan7 koh-khah siong-tiong7; sou2-i2 goa2 phah-sng3 tek-khak m7-thang lau5 teh; lau5 teh,eng2 u7 e7-kun. Chhin-chhiuN7 cheng5 ti7 E7-mng5 u7 chit8 lang5 ai3 lai5 than3 to7-li2 jip8 kau3-hoe7, iau2-ku2 thiaN kau3-hoe7 kong2 m7-thang chhai7 bok8-chu2; i-e5 sim bo5 beng5-pek8 chit e5 bok8-chu2 e5 to7-li2, phah-sng3 bok8-chu2 i2-keng hau3 chiah ku2, tek-khak u7 sin5 ti7-teh, m7-si7 chhin-chhiuN7 peng5-siong5 e5 chha5, sou2-i2 chiong kui-kham e5 bok8-chu2 it-chin7 koaN7-khi3 soaN-teng2 tai5 ti7 bong7-nih8. Che si7 hian2-beng5 u7 gi5-ngai2 khian3-sng2 e5 sim. Sou2-i2 koh bo5 joa7-ku2 tu2-tioh8 chhi3-lian7, chiu7 si7-soa7 chau2 khi3 soaN-teng2, kut8 hiah-e5 bok8-chu2 koh to3-lai5 pai3, lai5 hok8-sai7. Au7-lai5 long2 bo5 thang ng3-bang7 i koh lai5 hoan2-hoe2; in-ui7 ¡§Kng hut-jian5 am3, hit e5 am3 si7 toa7.¡¨ Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni thang chai e7-kun tek-khak tioh8 tu5 hou7 i li7, chiah boe7 koh hoat. Tioh8 siuN7 kou2-cha2 e5 lang5 siat bok8-chu2, si7 beh hou7 lang5 ki3-liam7, m7-si7 beh hou7 lang5 pai3; iau2-ku2 au7-lai5 long2 khi3 pai3, khi3 hok8-sai7--i. Ho5-hong3 chit-si5 e5 bok8-chu2, se3-siok8 i2-keng pun2 teh hok8-sai7 keng3-pai3; kiam2 m7-si7 koh khah khoai3 be5-hek8 au7-lai5 e5 lang5, long2 khi3 pai3 khi3 hok8-sai7 i mah? Sou2-i2 tek-khak m7-thang chhiaN2 lau5 teh. Cha hian7-si5 u7 chit ho7 bok8-chu2 e5 mia5, 